parser

类 Table

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.Table

  • class Table
extends java.lang.Object
    Operator precedence table. Note that the entries in the table may not be what it exactly should be. Some error detectations are implemented by filling some entries with '<' or '>' so that during reducing the errors can be detected.

    • 方法详细资料

      • get

        public java.lang.String get(java.lang.String left,
                            java.lang.String right)
                     throws exceptions.MissingRightParenthesisException,
                            exceptions.TrinaryOperationException
        Get the entry index by left and right.
        参数:
        left - represents the line
        right - represents the column
        返回:
        the content of the entry
        抛出:
        exceptions.MissingRightParenthesisException - if the expression miss a right parenthesis
        exceptions.TrinaryOperationException - if the expression has an error in using trinary operation
